'''''Make Love, Not War: The Sexual Revolution: An Unfettered History''''' is a 2001 book by [[David Allyn]].<ref>[https://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/boston/access/53818202.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=May+14%2C+2000&author=Scot+Lehigh%2C+Globe+Staff&pub=Boston+Globe&desc=EVERYTHING+YOU+ALWAYS+WANTED+TO+KNOW+ABOUT+THE+SEXUAL+REVOLUTION*+*BUT+PROBABLY+DIDN%27T+ASK&pqatl=google EVERYTHING YOU ALWAYS WANTED TO KNOW ABOUT THE SEXUAL REVOLUTION* *BUT PROBABLY DIDN'T ASK], ''[[The Boston Globe]]''</ref>
